<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6264058>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. A. Kalliapseudes obtusifrons, terminal spiniform seta of mandibular palp. B; Kalliapseudes profundus n. sp., terminal spiniform seta of mandibular palp. C. Kalliapseudes tomiokaensis, pleotelson modified after Shiino (1966). D. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., pleotelson. E. Kalliapseudes bamberi n. sp., pleotelson. F. Kalliapseudes dongarae n. sp., pleotelson. G. Kalliapseudes gutui n. sp., pereopod 2 dactylus. H. Kalliapseudes tomiokaensis, pereopod 2 dactylus modified after Shiino (1966). I. Kalliapseudes bamberi n. sp., pereopod 6 dactylus. J. Kalliapseudes tomiokaensis, pereopod 6 dactylus modified after Shiino (1966)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6264058/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6264062>
    dc:description "FIGURE 45. A. Kalliapseudes profundus n. sp., pereopod 5. B. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., pereopod 5. C. Kalliapseudes profundus n. sp., pereopod 6. D. Kalliapseudes dongarae n. sp., pereopod 6. E. Kalliapseudes longisetosus, pereopod 3. F. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., pereopod 3. G. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., rostrum. H. Kalliapseudes magnus, rostrum. I. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., mandibular palp. J. Kalliapseudes profundus n. sp., mandibular palp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6264062/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6264066>
    dc:description "FIGURE 46. A. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., male antennule. B. Kalliapseudes gutui n. sp., male antennule. C. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., pereopod 1. D. Kalliapseudes gutui n. sp., cheliped exopodite. E. Kalliapseudes langi, pereopod 1 modified after Guţu (2006). F. Kalliapseudes langi, dorsal view of body modified after Guţu (2006). G. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., dorsal view of body. H. Kalliapseudes mauritanicus, pereopod 1. I. Kalliapseudes quadrirobustirostris n. sp., pereopod 1. J. Kalliapseudes mauritanicus, female antennule. K. Kalliapseudes magnus, female antennule." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6264066/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6264072>
    dc:description "FIGURE 47. A. Kalliapseudes messingi, male pereopod 6. B. Kalliapseudes gutui n. sp., male pereopod 6. C. Kalliapseudes magnus, female pereopod 6. D. Kalliapseudes dongarae n. sp., male pereopod 6. E. Kalliapseudes dongarae n. sp., antenna. F. Kalliapseudes gutui n. sp., antenna. G. Kalliapseudes dongarae n. sp., pereopod 5. H. Kalliapseudes syntresis n. sp., pereopod 5." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6264072/files/figure.png" ;
